data.description: Here's your chance to purchase a modernized farmhouse and acreage that embodies country living with upgraded, stylish finishes! Built in 1896 and sprawling across 1.63 acres, this property features 4 bedrooms plus a bonus room, 1 full bathroom, over 2,000 square feet, and a 1.5 car detached garage. 163' well, submersible pump, and pressure tank were completed approximately 12 years ago. Enjoy  rehab work completed within the last 6 years as well as the benefits of 360-degree farm fields surrounding the property, for the utmost privacy and scenic views! In addition, the mature trees surrounding the property are a rare and picture-perfect find. Spend upcoming fall mornings on the spacious and inviting front porch. The backyard features the opportunity to raise your own livestock, with a chicken coup included. The ample grass space provides the opportunity to have the backyard oasis of your dreams! The long, gravel drive leads to the garage and fenced-in green space. Heading inside, the main level boasts a formal dining room, spacious family room, wood-burning stove to cozy up to this fall and winter, bonus room that can be utilized as an office or playroom, and an updated full bathroom fit for a magazine. In addition, the updated kitchen comes complete with a walk-in pantry and butler's quarters space, shiplap accents, modernized shelving, a farmhouse sink, butcherblock countertops, shaker cabinetry, custom range hood, and a mudroom that leads to the backyard. The second floor offers 4 roomy bedrooms, barn door accents, and an exceptional Edison bulb chandelier! Located within the Dwight School District. Property being sold AS-IS. Call today to schedule your private showing!
